{
  "texts": [
    "For the MSQ, although the control group had lower scores across all weeks (including baseline), the group × week interaction was not significant (main effect of group on MSQ: β = -1.688, p = 0.024; group × week effect on MSQ: β = 0.041, p = 0.678) which suggests that sleep symptoms improved at a similar rate for both groups",
    "Recognizing that overall group comparisons might mask the effects of individual engagement with specific app features, we investigated whether engagement with certain features predicted different degrees of symptom reduction.",
    "A key feature of the genAI-enabled app is the \"guided sessions,\" which provide clinical personalization achievable only through the integration of domain-specific AI tailored to mental health.",
    "This feature allows users to explore specific issues or challenges they are experiencing through guided questioning.",
    "The chatbot -enhanced by specialized clinical machine learning algorithms designed explicitly for mental health applications -identifies core psychological mechanisms underlying the user's problems."
  ]
}